            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De increpatione et reprehensione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
      ¶ De increpatione et reprehen
      <lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>sione. Rubrica. 5.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/> <ref>SAlomon in prouerb. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e127">Qui odit
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>increpationes insipiens est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e133"> 
         / <ref>15. c.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e135">Qui acquiescit increpationibus pos
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>sessor est cordis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e144"> 
        / <ref>Idem in ecclefiast. c. 7.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e146">Melius est a sapiente corripi quam astuta a
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>dulatione dec ipi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>¶ <ref>Terentius in andria. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e158">Obsequium ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>cos: veritas odium parit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>¶ <ref>Tullius de oratore li. i. in fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e168">Malo non in
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>telligi orationem meam quam reprehendi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e174"> 
        / <ref>Li. 2</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e176">Homines imperiti facilius quod stulte dixe
        <lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>ris reprehendere: quam quod sapienter tulleris
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>laudare possunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>¶ <ref>Mattheus in euangel. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e190">Quid vides
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>festucam in oculo fratris. tui: et trabem in
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>oculo tuo non vides. Aut quomodo dicis
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>fratri tuo: frater: sine eijciam festucam de ocu
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>lo tuo: ecce trabes in oculo tuo est. hypo
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>crita eijce prius trabem de oculo tuo: et tuno
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>videbis eijcere festucam de oculo fratris tui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e207">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>
               <ref>/ Idem dicit lucas in euang. c. 6. </ref> <!--no quote-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e216">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>¶ <ref>Paulus apostolus epistola. i. ad timothe
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>um. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e220">Seniorem ne increpaueris: sed ob
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>secra vt patrem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e228">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>¶ <ref>Seneca in prouerbiis:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e232">Crudelis est in re
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>aduersa obiurgatio. Obiurgationi semper
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>aliquid blanditie admisce.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e240">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>¶ <ref>Ualerius inaximus vel. 3 ti. de fiducia sui.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e244">Euripides quidem atthenis arrogans vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>sus non est: cum postulante populo vt ex tra
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>gedia sententiam quandam tolleret progres
        <lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>sus in senatum dixit: se vt populum doceret non
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>vt ab eo discederet fabulas componere sol <!--174.xml-->
                 <pb ed="#V" n="68-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>lennes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e267"> 
        / <ref>Li. 4. ti. de verecundila:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e269">Athenis
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>quidam vltime senectutis cum spectatum
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>ludos in theatrum venisset cunque nemo ex
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>cuilibet sessum reciperet ad lacedemonio
        <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>rum legatos peruenit: qui homines etate
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>modica canos eius in annos assurgendi of
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>ficio venerati sunt: sedemque ei inter ipos
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>honoratissimo loco dderunt: quod vbi fieri po
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>pulus aspexit maximo plausu aliene vrbis
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>verecundiam comprobabat. Fertur tunc vnum
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>ex lacedemoniis dixisse erga athenienses quid
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>sit rectum sciunt: sed id facere negligunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e296">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>¶ <ref>Marcialis cocus vel vndique suscepto. c. 3.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e300">Cur maculas alios maculosior omnibus al
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>bi: Et carpi dignus carpere non metuis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>/ <ref>Captlo. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e312">Fratris verrucas mordaci de
        <lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>te refringis. Ulcera dissimulans ique tib
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>in ore sedent. Ad fratris culpam aquile tu
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>lumina portas. Ad tua cum scelera nulla vel
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>orba feras.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e325"> 
        / <ref>Capitulo. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e327">Alterius censor:
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>censor et esto tuus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e333">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>¶ <ref>Auctor scilict de for. honeste vite. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e337">Repre
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>henderis patienter. Si merito te obiurga
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>uerit aliquis scito quod profuitus. si immerito
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>scito quod prodesse voluit. Non esto acerbus
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>reprehensor.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e349">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>¶ <ref>Cato capistolo. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e353">Que culpare soles ea tu ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>feceris ipse. Turpe est edoceri cum culpa re
        <lb ed="#V" n="29" break="no"/>darguit ipsum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-d1e361">
               <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>¶ <ref>Montenarius in luna cleri. c. 128. et p.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d55951-Qd1e365">Di ligitur tector scelerum reprehensor oditur.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
